    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "县官",
        "胡子林",
        "青袍甲"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四青袍、县官同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "做官不在大小，只要赚钱就好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我，清河县县官是也。自到任以来，官清民顺。今当三六九日，放告之期。"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来呀，将放告牌抬出。"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（胡子林上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡子林",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "冤枉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回禀老爷：有人喊冤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "问问他为什么喊冤？"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷问你为什么喊冤？"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡子林",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我叫胡子林，只因我的儿子胡抡忤逆不孝，特来求太爷责备于他。"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他叫胡子林，就是胡老好，送他的儿子胡抡忤逆不孝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，原来为的是他老人家的事呀。来呀，拿我这一枝火签，交给他，就说我们"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这儿有个乡风，叫做原告传被告。叫他拿了这一枝火签，去把被告传了来，本"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "县替他审问就是啦。退堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（县官下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太爷吩咐下来啦：这有火签一枝，交给你。我们这地方有一个乡风，叫做原告"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "传被告。你拿火签将被告传了来，我们老爷就替你审问。你去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（胡子林接签。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡子林",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，叫老汉自己去传他么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是叫你自己去传他去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡子林",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他若是不肯来呢？"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他若不肯来，你只管打着他，也把他打了来啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡子林",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，是是是。如此，待我去传他去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "青袍甲→胡子林",
          "turns": 5
        },
        {
          "edge": "胡子林→青袍甲",
          "turns": 4
