    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "山西人",
        "胡子林",
        "胡抡"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（山西人上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曲曲弯弯路，重重叠叠门。雁飞不到处，断不了咱山西人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我，曹老西，山西太原人。只因父母双亡，家道不好，这两年又遭了荒年，在"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家中实实难以度日，因此来到了清河县，要投奔我舅舅。不想他已于前年得病"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "而亡。是我在此地，一无亲戚，二无朋友，走投无路，就凑了几百铜钱，贩了"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "些个沙锅，在街上去卖。今天也不早了，待我挑起担子到街坊上去卖便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "南梆子慢板",
          "musical_style": "南梆子慢板",
          "style_family": "南梆子",
          "text": "我老西生来命运薄，"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "南梆子慢板",
          "musical_style": "南梆子慢板",
          "style_family": "南梆子",
          "text": "幼年间无爹娘受了奔波。"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "南梆子慢板",
          "musical_style": "南梆子慢板",
          "style_family": "南梆子",
          "text": "因此上投舅父来到了清河。"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "实指望到此间他帮衬于我，"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "又谁知身得病他命见阎罗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "无计奈做生意贩卖沙锅。"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卖沙锅！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（胡抡上，胡子林追上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡子林",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我把你这个奴才，我送了你忤逆了，你还不同我去见太爷去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡抡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见官我可是不敢去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡子林",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不敢去也得要去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡抡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我可是真不能去，看你把我怎么样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡子林",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不去，我就打你这个奴才！"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡抡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打我我也是不去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（胡子林持拐杖打，山西人闯过，胡子林打沙锅破，胡抡跑下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你把沙锅给打了，可不能走了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡子林",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀大哥！"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大锅小号的，已打了两套了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡子林",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老汉一时失手了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你试手？你要不试手，把我的锅只怕就都打完了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡子林",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓大哥，我不是竟意呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不成敬意，你要都给我打碎了，只怕就成了敬意了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡子林",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要求你方便方便，恕我之罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不行不行，我的锅就是我老子的命，你把我老子的锅打破了，咱是非打官司不"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "行！"
        },
        {
          "character": "胡子林",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大哥，休要动怒，待老汉设法赔你几文，也就是了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不行，非打官司不行。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（山西人拉胡子林同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "山西人→胡子林",
