    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "县官",
        "山西人",
        "青袍甲"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四青袍、县官同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我为县正堂，黎民定遭殃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来呀，胡老头儿带的被告儿带来了靡有吓？"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尚未带来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去到衙门口去看一看去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（山西人拉胡子林同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到了，到了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷正在问你呢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫原告堂外候传，先带被告。"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷叫你堂外候传，先带你上堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（青袍甲拉山西人跪。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大老爷，小人冤枉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好你个胡抡呐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人不敢胡论。"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你老爹养你一场，为的是什么？你为什么不孝顺他？你与我从实地讲！"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他打了我的锅，我过不了吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呸！他打你，你过不了？你就是过不了，也要想法子养活他呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人是没有本钱的呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这话更是放屁！一个人养活老亲，还说是什么有本钱无本钱。"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人是实实担不了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "担不了也要孝顺父母。"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要求大老爷公断。"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你大胆！"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "有胡抡上堂来我用目观定，"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我看你这个人，断不是好人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人是个老实人呐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是个老实人？这么办罢，老爷赏赏你罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷要赏小人，好，你赏我多少吧？"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我赏你四十。"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "太少了。你老人家多赏我点罢。赏我二百罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这个样子，只怕受不起。四十我看你也就很够你受用的了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你老人家再添上一添，赏我一百罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一百也怕受不了，赏你八十罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "趴下！"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "趴下做什么呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老爷要打你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳呀老爷呀！你老人家打我做啥呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我老爷打你一个不孝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人一肚子冤枉，你还要打我，我是怎能得笑？"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大胆！"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "叫声胡抡太欺情，"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我一肚子的冤屈，要赏我钱，我还不够本。怎么还要打我？我是一个异乡人吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀呀呸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "说什么你是异乡人，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（青袍甲推倒山西人，打。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一十，二十，三十，四十。"
        },
        {
          "character": "山西人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大老爷，小人是个异乡人吓！老爷恩典呐！"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好大胆子，还敢狡赖。再打！"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "五十，六十，七十，八十！"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦，打死了？拖了出去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四青袍同抬山西人下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，退堂。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四青袍同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想本县，今日在二堂之上，将这胡抡打死，但是人命关天，必须要详禀上司，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（山西人上，站县官身旁哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "清河县在书房把本修上，"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "谁知他禁不起一命身亡。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（山西人捏县官喉。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗳呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "一霎时只觉得头晕心慌。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（县官吹须，山西人退。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我这里战兢兢把后堂来上，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（县官转场，吐。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "等候了明日里再做主张。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（山西人捏县官喉，县官颤抖，山西人捏。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "县官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你算了罢，别招骂啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（县官、山西人同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（完）"
        }
      ],
